  <entry>
    <title>在termux上安装octave</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2020/03/22/%E5%9C%A8termux%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85octave/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2020/03/22/%E5%9C%A8termux%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85octave/</id>
    <published>2020-03-22T12:35:12.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-03-24T05:04:57.320Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>手机借助 <code>termux</code> 安装 <code>octave</code> ，可在手机实现科学计算</p><h1 id="添加-GNU-软件源"><a href="#添加-GNU-软件源" class="headerlink" title="添加 GNU 软件源"></a>添加 GNU 软件源</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg install curl gnupg</span><br><span class="line">curl -LO https://its-pointless.github.io/setup-pointless-repo.sh </span><br><span class="line">bash setup-pointless-repo.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果不成功，换用</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir -p <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$PREFIX</span>/etc/apt/sources.list.d/"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"deb https://its-pointless.github.io/files/ termux extras"</span> &gt; <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$PREFIX</span>/etc/apt/sources.list.d/pointless.list"</span></span><br><span class="line">curl <span class="string">"https://its-pointless.github.io/pointless.gpg"</span> | apt-key add</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装-octave"><a href="#安装-octave" class="headerlink" title="安装 octave"></a>安装 octave</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg install octave</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果想让 <code>octave</code> 链接 <code>jupyter</code> ， 安装内核</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install octave-kernel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="完成！"><a href="#完成！" class="headerlink" title="完成！"></a>完成！</h1>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;p&gt;手机借助 &lt;code&gt;termux&lt;/code&gt; 安装 &lt;code&gt;octave&lt;/code&gt; ，可在手机实现科学计算&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;添加-GNU-软件源&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#添加-GNU-软件源&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;添加 GN
      
    
    </summary>
    
    
