  <entry>
    <title>在termux上安装python</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2020/03/22/%E5%9C%A8termux%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85python/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2020/03/22/%E5%9C%A8termux%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85python/</id>
    <published>2020-03-22T12:20:41.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-03-24T05:04:51.360Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>通过termux可以将python 安装到手机上，随身查看并编写脚本</p><h1 id="安装-python"><a href="#安装-python" class="headerlink" title="安装 python"></a>安装 python</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg instll python</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果安装 <code>python2</code> ,将命令<code>pkg instll python</code> 改为 <code>pkg instll python2</code></p><h2 id="升级pip版本"><a href="#升级pip版本" class="headerlink" title="升级pip版本"></a>升级pip版本</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python -m pip install --upgrade pip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>对应的<code>python2</code> 为 </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python2 -m pip install --upgrade pip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安装-ipython"><a href="#安装-ipython" class="headerlink" title="安装 ipython"></a>安装 ipython</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg install clang</span><br><span class="line">pip install ipython</span><br><span class="line">pip3.6 install ipython</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="优化vim"><a href="#优化vim" class="headerlink" title="优化vim"></a>优化vim</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg install vim-python</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安装科学计算包"><a href="#安装科学计算包" class="headerlink" title="安装科学计算包"></a>安装科学计算包</h2><ul><li><code>jupyter</code></li><li><code>numpy</code></li><li><code>matplotlib</code></li></ul><h3 id="首先安装依赖"><a href="#首先安装依赖" class="headerlink" title="首先安装依赖"></a>首先安装依赖</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt install python python-dev clang fftw libzmq libzmq-dev freetype freetype-dev libpng libpng-dev pkg-config</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>有些 <code>-dev</code> 可能会安装失败， 这没问题～ 继续</p><h3 id="安装-jupyter"><a href="#安装-jupyter" class="headerlink" title="安装 jupyter"></a>安装 jupyter</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">LDFLAGS=<span class="string">" -lm -lcompiler_rt"</span> pip install jupyter</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="juypter-默认文件配置"><a href="#juypter-默认文件配置" class="headerlink" title="juypter 默认文件配置"></a>juypter 默认文件配置</h4><p>创建密码</p><p>终端输入 <code>ipython</code> 启动，随后依次输入</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from notebook.auth import passwd</span><br><span class="line">passwd()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建密码并确认后记录<code>sha1</code>秘钥值，如 <code>&#39;sha1:XXXXXXX&#39;</code></p><p>生成默认配置文件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">jupyter notebook --generate-config</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在生成的 <code>./.jupyter/jupyter_notebook_config.py</code> 配置文件中，采用命令 <code>vi .jupyter/jupyter_notebook_config.py</code> 进入文件，按<code>i</code>进入编辑状态修改以下几项内容</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">c.NotebookApp.allow_remote_access = True</span><br><span class="line">c.NotebookApp.ip = <span class="string">'*'</span></span><br><span class="line">c.NotebookApp.port = 8000</span><br><span class="line">c.NotebookApp.password = u<span class="string">'sha1:XXXXXXX'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输入 <code>:wq</code> 保存并退出，启动 <code>jupyter</code> </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">jupyter notebook</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>随后可在本机浏览器中输入 <code>127.0.0.1：8000</code> 或局域网中输入 <code>ip:8000</code> 打开</p><h3 id="安装-numpy"><a href="#安装-numpy" class="headerlink" title="安装 numpy"></a>安装 numpy</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">LDFLAGS=<span class="string">" -lm -lcompiler_rt"</span> pip install numpy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装-matplotlib"><a href="#安装-matplotlib" class="headerlink" title="安装 matplotlib"></a>安装 matplotlib</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">LDFLAGS=<span class="string">" -lm -lcompiler_rt"</span> pip install matplotlib</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意 <code>numpy</code> 是 <code>matplotlib</code> 的依赖包， 二者不能同时安装</p><h1 id="完成！"><a href="#完成！" class="headerlink" title="完成！"></a>完成！</h1>]]></content>
    
